Herdr behavior reference
------------------------

This project reimplements Herdr-like agent status and notification concepts for
tmux from public behavior and architecture descriptions, with a clean-room Rust
implementation. Herdr is AGPL-3.0-or-later/commercial dual-licensed; no Herdr
source code or bundled manifests are copied here.

  https://github.com/ogulcancelik/herdr

Tmux plugin conventions
-----------------------

Some shell wrapper and option-helper patterns follow common TPM/tmux plugin
conventions. Earlier research also reviewed tmux-sidebar's MIT-licensed plugin
shape:

  https://github.com/tmux-plugins/tmux-sidebar

